<item>
 <title>Drupal Performance Optimization Options &amp; Checklist</title>
 <link>http://badcamp-2015.kbox/session/drupal-performance-optimization-options-checklist</link>
 <description>&lt;div class=&quot;body field&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;As great as Drupal can be, it doesn&#039;t scale well for Web sites with a lot of content and/or a lot of users. To make it perform better under these scenarios, it&#039;s necessary to make use of several strategies, tools and techniques.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;By attending this session, you&#039;ll develop an understanding of what the options are in making your Drupal site more performant. So when you run into performance-related issues, you&#039;ll have an idea of where to begin.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;I plan to cover the following areas:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Configuration Best Practices&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Views Caching&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;System Administration&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Cache Replacements&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Caching and Optimizing Specific Components&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;External Caching&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Cache Warming / Priming&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Services&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Drupal-Specific Hosting&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Tools&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Useful References&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;I&#039;ll explain why there is no one-size-fits-all approach (i.e. don&#039;t solve problems you don&#039;t have), give examples of how to look into specific issues, get into the details of the above items, and share some experiences with recent projects. Also, I&#039;m hoping to leave some time for discussion during the question period.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field field-name-field-session-track field-type-taxonomy-term-reference field-label-inline clearfix field-wrapper&quot;&gt;&lt;h2 class=&quot;field-label&quot;&gt;Session track: &lt;/h2&gt;&lt;ul class=&quot;links inline&quot;&gt;&lt;li class=&quot;taxonomy-term-reference-0&quot; class=&quot;field-item even&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/tracks/devops-performance&quot;&gt;DevOps + Performance&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field field-name-field-session-skill-level field-type-taxonomy-term-reference field-label-inline clearfix field-wrapper&quot;&gt;&lt;h2 class=&quot;field-label&quot;&gt;Session skill level: &lt;/h2&gt;&lt;ul class=&quot;links inline&quot;&gt;&lt;li class=&quot;taxonomy-term-reference-0&quot; class=&quot;field-item even&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/skill-level/beginner&quot;&gt;Beginner&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field field-name-field-session-speaker field-type-entityreference field-label-inline clearfix field-wrapper&quot;&gt;&lt;div  class=&quot;field-label&quot;&gt;Session speaker(s):&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;textformatter-list&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/users/colan&quot; class=&quot;user user-904 entityreference&quot;&gt;colan&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
