 <title>Drupal hosting options and performance improvements</title>
 <link>http://badcamp-2015.kbox/session/drupal-hosting-options-and-performance-improvements</link>
 <description>&lt;div class=&quot;body field&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;Learn how to choose from the variety of hosting levels and provider offerings. There are a myriad of options from shared hosting, VPS, managed instances, dedicated servers, and Drupal-specific providers.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;What are the important indicators you have, so that you can choose the most appropriate option? Can you really do more with less? What level of access do you need in order to get the best site performance?&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This session will cover the range from one-click installs to setting up your own environment and a number of options in between&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field field-name-field-session-track field-type-taxonomy-term-reference field-label-inline clearfix field-wrapper&quot;&gt;&lt;h2 class=&quot;field-label&quot;&gt;Session track: &lt;/h2&gt;&lt;ul class=&quot;links inline&quot;&gt;&lt;li class=&quot;taxonomy-term-reference-0&quot; class=&quot;field-item even&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/tracks/devops-performance&quot;&gt;DevOps + Performance&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field field-name-field-session-skill-level field-type-taxonomy-term-reference field-label-inline clearfix field-wrapper&quot;&gt;&lt;h2 class=&quot;field-label&quot;&gt;Session skill level: &lt;/h2&gt;&lt;ul class=&quot;links inline&quot;&gt;&lt;li class=&quot;taxonomy-term-reference-0&quot; class=&quot;field-item even&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/skill-level/beginner&quot;&gt;Beginner&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field field-name-field-session-speaker field-type-entityreference field-label-inline clearfix field-wrapper&quot;&gt;&lt;div  class=&quot;field-label&quot;&gt;Session speaker(s):&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;textformatter-list&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/users/slovak&quot; class=&quot;user user-177 entityreference&quot;&gt;Slovak&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
