<item>
 <title>An Introduction to Containers</title>
 <link>http://badcamp-2015.kbox/session/introduction-containers</link>
 <description>&lt;div class=&quot;body field&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;You&#039;ve heard the term &quot;containers.&quot; Maybe you&#039;ve heard the buzz surrounding new technologies like Docker and CoreOS. They plaster the front pages of HackerNews, reddit and the blogosphere. &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you&#039;ve wondered just what the big deal is and what they are, this is a what, why, and a how-to for Drupal containerization for those new to the technology.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Simply put, containerization enables you to scale your apps with increasing ease. For developers, it&#039;s a step towards abstracting away your infrastructure so you can stop worrying about developing, testing, and running in identical environments - it&#039;s all the same inside your container.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;In this session, we&#039;ll emphasize an understanding of what containers are, what they do, and how they&#039;re different from a virtual machine. We&#039;ll end with getting a simple Drupal container app up and running.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field field-name-field-session-track field-type-taxonomy-term-reference field-label-inline clearfix field-wrapper&quot;&gt;&lt;h2 class=&quot;field-label&quot;&gt;Session track: &lt;/h2&gt;&lt;ul class=&quot;links inline&quot;&gt;&lt;li class=&quot;taxonomy-term-reference-0&quot; class=&quot;field-item even&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/tracks/devops-performance&quot;&gt;DevOps + Performance&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field field-name-field-session-skill-level field-type-taxonomy-term-reference field-label-inline clearfix field-wrapper&quot;&gt;&lt;h2 class=&quot;field-label&quot;&gt;Session skill level: &lt;/h2&gt;&lt;ul class=&quot;links inline&quot;&gt;&lt;li class=&quot;taxonomy-term-reference-0&quot; class=&quot;field-item even&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/skill-level/beginner&quot;&gt;Beginner&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field field-name-field-session-speaker field-type-entityreference field-label-inline clearfix field-wrapper&quot;&gt;&lt;div  class=&quot;field-label&quot;&gt;Session speaker(s):&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;textformatter-list&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/users/gabesullice&quot; class=&quot;user user-179 entityreference&quot;&gt;gabesullice&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
 <pubDate>Mon, 14 Sep 2015 16:32:09 +0000</pubDate>
