<item>
 <title>Introduction to DevOps</title>
 <link>http://badcamp-2015.kbox/session/introduction-devops</link>
 <description>&lt;div class=&quot;body field&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;&quot;DevOps&quot; isn&#039;t exactly &quot;new&quot; anymore, neither is it universally implemented. If you have not yet implemented DevOps, attend this beginner session to learn the answers to questions like:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;What is DevOps?&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Why is DevOps a thing now?&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;What did people / organizations do before there was DevOps?&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;What are people / organizations doing who are NOT doing DevOps now?&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;If DevOps is so great, why &lt;strong&gt;isn&#039;t&lt;/strong&gt; everybody doing DevOps?&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;How much does it cost to do DevOps?&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Is DevOps just for enterprise level shops?&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;What&#039;s the difference between Continuous Integration / Continuous Delivery / Continuous Deployment?&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Do I have to learn version control to do DevOps?&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;What&#039;s a provisioner and do I have to set one up to be able to do DevOps?&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;How do I get started with DevOps?&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;When you leave this session, you will have&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;an understanding of how DevOps can benefit you&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;a strong grasp of the terminology used in relation to DevOps and a basic understanding of what it means&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;a set of actionable items from which to choose to continue your education in DevOps&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;Whether you live in the &quot;Dev&quot;, &quot;Ops&quot; or &quot;other&quot; world you are welcome to attend and learn! No prior knowledge of DevOps is required.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field field-name-field-session-track field-type-taxonomy-term-reference field-label-inline clearfix field-wrapper&quot;&gt;&lt;h2 class=&quot;field-label&quot;&gt;Session track: &lt;/h2&gt;&lt;ul class=&quot;links inline&quot;&gt;&lt;li class=&quot;taxonomy-term-reference-0&quot; class=&quot;field-item even&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/tracks/devops-performance&quot;&gt;DevOps + Performance&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field field-name-field-session-skill-level field-type-taxonomy-term-reference field-label-inline clearfix field-wrapper&quot;&gt;&lt;h2 class=&quot;field-label&quot;&gt;Session skill level: &lt;/h2&gt;&lt;ul class=&quot;links inline&quot;&gt;&lt;li class=&quot;taxonomy-term-reference-0&quot; class=&quot;field-item even&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/skill-level/beginner&quot;&gt;Beginner&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field field-name-field-session-speaker field-type-entityreference field-label-inline clearfix field-wrapper&quot;&gt;&lt;div  class=&quot;field-label&quot;&gt;Session speaker(s):&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;textformatter-list&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/users/vegantriathlete&quot; class=&quot;user user-639 entityreference&quot;&gt;vegantriathlete&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
