 <description>&lt;div class=&quot;body field&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;As the Support Manager for Kalamuna, I constantly get requests to “please make my Drupal Site faster.”  After many years of trial and error, I’ve discovered how to honor this request.&lt;/p&gt;
